  • DOGE team enters the CFPB. Staff is reportedly very mad. Later in the day Elon tweets "CFPB RIP" so I guess the staff is extra mad now.

  • President Trump says that DOGE will be identifying the illegals that are getting social security and removing them from the program

  • President Trump fires the board of the Kennedy center via Truth Social post on his way to Mar-A-Lago, appoints himself chairman, and says that the drag shows targeting children will STOP.

  • President Trump signs a 2nd amendment EO ordering DOJ to review all of Biden's anti-gun actions

  • President Trump revokes Joe Biden's security clearance and stops his daily intelligence briefing (clearly that wasn't working) because Biden is senile and can't be trusted with sensitive information, and also because Biden did it to him first. Also has it tweeted from the White House account @ Biden's personal X account so that he would get notified by his old house that he was fired.

  • President Trump has also fired the head of the National Archives and Records Administration.
